      <title>船舶堆积导致液化天然气运费跌至历史最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/lng-freight-rates-plunge-to-record-low-levels-as-vessels-pile-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场面临船舶过剩的问题，液化天然气运输成本大幅下降，这一发展可能为天然气进口商带来缓解，并有助于增加贸易商的利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/lng-freight-rates-plunge-to-record-low-levels-as-vessels-pile-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 02:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
